Google Translate:
About website
Welcome to Affärsverkens website. On this website, you will find information about the products and the services that we offer. There is also information about different ways you can get in contact with us.
Browser/Screen reader
Our website is optimized for Internet Explorer version 10.0 and above. The website also supports Safari, Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox and on browsers for smartphones and tablets with iOS and Android. The latest software will increase the experience when using the website.
JavaScript
This website uses JavaScript
Responsive website
This website is responsive and it will adapt according to the device that is being used to optimize the experience depending on the device that is used. This also means that some information or images will be prioritized or concealed depending on the device that is used.
Customize the browser according to your need
If you think the size of the text on the website is too small, you can change this in the browser. The way to change this varies between web browsers but it is common to be able to do this from the settings in the View menu.
How we use cookies
We use cookies to analyse visitor statistics and to manage sign in and settings. Google Analytics which is a web analysis tool used on this website uses cookies. Cookies collect information about how visitors use the website, where the visitors are coming from and the total amount of visits to improve the website and to be able to provide a better user experience. If you do not accept cookies, no information will be collected.
If you do not wish cookies to be stored on your computer, you can change the settings yourself on the browser so that it does not save cookies. The web browsers help page will have more information about this.
Privacy policy
It is important to us at Affärsverken that you feel safe with how we manage your personal information. Therefore, we are open about how we collect, manage and share the information that we collect about you.
In connection to the Data Protection Regulations, GDPR, we have updated our privacy policy. The privacy policy handles you as a private person in a business relationship with Affärsverken.
In this policy you will find information about which personal data that we collect, how we collect the personal data, what we use the personal data for, how long we save the personal data, to whom we give out the personal data, how we protect the personal data and your rights. It also consist information about the person that is responsible for the handling of the personal data and the data protection representative.
Affärsverken Karlskrona AB is responsible for the personal data that we manage about our customers. This responsibility includes the subsidiaries Affärsverken Elnät AB and Affärsverken Energi AB. You can contact us if you have any questions regarding the privacy policy or the data protection policy by sending us an email to
dataskydd@affarsverken.se
.
You will find the full policy here (in Swedish):
Affärsverkens Integritetspolicy
Contact us
If you have any questions or feedback about our website, you can reach us by sending an email to
info@affarsverken.se
.
Follow us on social media
Welcome
